  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cradle of Nightmares: Flowers to You is an ATB turn-based game based on combat adventures made by RPGMaker.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will play as a high school student named Yue Qing, as the world is being torn apart by a mysterious phenomenon from outside the world, the \"White Light\", and you will start from the ordinary daily life and fall into the dark and gloomy \"Second World\", where you will embark on a journey to find your best friends, fight against the madmen under the invasion of emptiness, and finally end the filthy fate of mankind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>~Fall into darkness at the moment~</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Soul-mimicking gameplay system</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>With the \"flower basket\" as the node, the map exploration is carried out in a propulsive manner, as well as the appropriate shortcut and regional connectivity design</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In battle, accumulate special skills with basic attack/defense/skills, and release strong attack skills to turn the tide</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The main and secondary hands cooperate with the strike, the attribute restraint of spells, the backstab system, etc</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/25c53a737ba8814082bb4042d9b095f7.poster.avif?t=1756425772\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/25c53a737ba8814082bb4042d9b095f7.webm?t=1756425772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/25c53a737ba8814082bb4042d9b095f7.mp4?t=1756425772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>~Thoughts converge into light~</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Rich weapon skill design</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A skill set with 2~5 skills as a weapon, rich loadout slots, off-hands, and spells</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Turn-based but unique battle mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The enemy/player swing back and forth design reduces the unpredictability of the traditional turn-based system and strengthens the player's sense of grasp of the battle</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/015f10e32c3709afa66194259dbbb011.poster.avif?t=1756425772\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/015f10e32c3709afa66194259dbbb011.webm?t=1756425772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/015f10e32c3709afa66194259dbbb011.mp4?t=1756425772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>~Ran, I am a round of the sun~</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Quite a wealth of maps, enemies, and boss battles to meet players' expectations for map exploration and fighting against strong enemies</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Plenty of plot and NPC side quests</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Special NPC frenzy battles</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple endings, multi-week inherited gameplay, and difficulty increases in the process</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/857ff062de987af72eaab0054ad45ece.poster.avif?t=1756425772\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/857ff062de987af72eaab0054ad45ece.webm?t=1756425772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/857ff062de987af72eaab0054ad45ece.mp4?t=1756425772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/4f5911ae64da37fe4518bb6f5f0b2386.poster.avif?t=1756425772\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/4f5911ae64da37fe4518bb6f5f0b2386.webm?t=1756425772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/4f5911ae64da37fe4518bb6f5f0b2386.mp4?t=1756425772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cradle of Nightmares: Flowers to You is an ATB turn-based game based on combat adventures made by RPGMaker.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will play as a high school student named Yue Qing, as the world is being torn apart by a mysterious phenomenon from outside the world, the \"White Light\", and you will start from the ordinary daily life and fall into the dark and gloomy \"Second World\", where you will embark on a journey to find your best friends, fight against the madmen under the invasion of emptiness, and finally end the filthy fate of mankind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>~Fall into darkness at the moment~</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Soul-mimicking gameplay system</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>With the \"flower basket\" as the node, the map exploration is carried out in a propulsive manner, as well as the appropriate shortcut and regional connectivity design</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In battle, accumulate special skills with basic attack/defense/skills, and release strong attack skills to turn the tide</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The main and secondary hands cooperate with the strike, the attribute restraint of spells, the backstab system, etc</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/25c53a737ba8814082bb4042d9b095f7.poster.avif?t=1756425772\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/25c53a737ba8814082bb4042d9b095f7.webm?t=1756425772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/25c53a737ba8814082bb4042d9b095f7.mp4?t=1756425772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></